snippet.title: A Soldier's Reaction. #Holiday #shorts
snippet.description:
A military officer attempts to hunt down a terrorist, destroy a terrorist gang and deactivate the sleeper cells under his command.
Cast - Akshay Kumar, Sonakshi Sinha, Freddy Daruwala 
Directed by - A.R. Murugadoss


"Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a high-octane action film which showcases Akshay Kumar's skills as an action star. The movie boasts of thrilling and intense action sequences, a well-written screenplay, and good performances from the lead actors. The plot of the movie revolves around the life of a soldier on vacation who stumbles upon a terrorist plot and decides to put a stop to it. He has to work with a local police officer and other officials to track down the terrorists and prevent them from carrying out their plan. The film also deals with themes of patriotism and selfless service to the nation. Overall, "Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a well-crafted action thriller that is sure to keep audiences on the edge of their seats.
#holiday #akshaykumar #sonakshisinha #govinda #freddydaruwala #soldier #shorts

Haan haan maalum
Hai hume bahut late ho gaya aane mein
Pure 10 nahi nahi 11 mahine lag gaye hume
Lekin tum log ko kya batau aisi fatti padi thi hum log ka kuch aisa project tha jisse plan karte karte karte 6-7 mahine aise nikle hume pata hi nai chala
Fir humne ye saal ka bigg boss dekha aur decide kiya abhi toh hum season 2 banaenge hi kaise bhi
Wo jo project hai jiski baat kar raha hu abhi back burner pe hai but promise hai hum usse kaise bhi aapke saamne laaenge😍

Abhi subah ke 6 baje main ye description bathroom mein likh raha hu seth log toh please deri ke lie maaf kar do baaki tum log hi seth ho mere dhani ho muje maalum hai naraazgi hogi lekin utna hi pyaar bhi karte ho
Chalo abhi video ka Favourite part comment karo aur apna fav dialogue bhi likh lo

Chalo abhi production ka batao is video ka

And ajay bhai jinhone teddy bear ka body double play kiya

snippet.title: Buffalo Sacrificed For 8 Year Old Goddess!! Nepal’s Newar People!!
snippet.description:
🎥 NEW CHANNEL ALERT!! » https://bit.ly/BestEverFoodClips 
💗 SUPPORT OUR MISSION » http://bit.ly/BestEverPatreon
📷 SAILESH BYANJANKAR » @NAAM.CHAINA
Like our music? Enjoy a free 30-day of Epidemic Sound for the best royalty-free music: http://share.epidemicsound.com/BEFRS 
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -  
1. KWACHA NEWARI RESTAURANT
ADDRESS: Chyasal, Belachhen road, Lalitpur, Nepal
🇳🇵BARA (LENTIL PANCAKE): Add mustard oil in a hot pan, then add pancake batter (mixture of flour and water). Add green onions, carrots, cumin powder, tomato, garlic cloves, and eggs. Cook on each side for 2 minutes.
🇳🇵CHATAMARI (NEPALI PIZZA): Add mustard oil in a hot pan, then add pancake batter (mixture of flour and water). Flatten batter with spoon, then add carrots, cucumbers, garlic cloves, tomato, coriander leaves, peas, and an egg.  Add salt, pepper, sesame and cumin powder.
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -  
2. KUMARI TEMPLE
ADDRESS: Lalitpur 09 Chyasal, Tin Mukhi Ganesh (Old Patan)
INTERVIEWEES: Niraj Ratna Bajracharya + Mohini Bajracharya
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -  
3. CHYASAL COMMUNITY SQUARE
ADDRESS:
🇳🇵KACHILA (MARINATED RAW MINCED MEAT): Mince buffalo meat, then season with salt, garlic, cumin seeds and red chili powder. Pound the mixture, then add fenugreek seeds. Add turmeric powder to hot oil, then pour onto the meat and mix well. Top with green onions.
🇳🇵NHYAPU (FRIED BUFFALO BRAIN): Boil innards & brain, then add mustard oil and turmeric powder. Fry until golden brown.
🇳🇵HE (FRIED BUFFALO BLOOD CLOT): Add buffalo blood to the pan. Stir until the blood clots.
🇳🇵SAPU MHICHA (BUFFALO TRIPE W/ BONE MARROW STUFFING): Take a piece of bone marrow and sew it in the tripe. Boil for 10-15 minutes. Drain the water, then fry. Add salt and cumin powder.
🇳🇵CHOILA (SPICY GRILLED BUFFALO MEAT): Grill buffalo meat on a woodfire, then chop meat into smaller pieces and add turmeric powder & chili powder.
🇳🇵ME (FRIED BUFFALO TONGUE): Boil tongue. Add mustard oil to a pan, turmeric powder, and tongue meat.
🇳🇵PUKALA (FRIED BUFFALO INNARDS): Boil innards. Add mustard oil to a pan, turmeric powder, and innards.
#BEFRS #BestEverFoodReviewShow #BestEverNepalTour 
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

Your contribution is an investment in the creative freedom of my channel and enables me to keep my content authentic and uninterrupted. Your donation allows me the time and resources to create more videos for you. We also have some pretty sweet rewards, exclusive to Patreon Bestys. » http://bit.ly/BestEverPatreon
 
Our VIP Patrons: Susanne Smarr, Jim Klingsporn, Leo Lui, Sam Cassidy, Venetia Edmunds, Jack Murray, Eimile Nakoma, Jack Li, Stephen Balasta, Louis Chisari, Ryan Rhodes, Paul Citulski, Matthew Holden, David Baliles, Jackson Li, John Logan and Summer & Grayson Stumpf.  
 
🥒 ABOUT BEFRS:
Hey, I’m Sonny! I’m from the US but I’ve been living in Asia for 10 years and started making food and travel videos to document my experiences. I travel to different parts of the world, hunting down and documenting the most unique food each country has to offer.
 
If you see any factual food errors in my videos, please feel free to politely let me know in the comments. I'm a huge fan of trying different, interesting foods in each country. My show is from a Western point of view, but more importantly, MY point of view. It is not meant to offend any person or culture.

snippet.description:
Meri Bassai is one of the longest and most popular Nepali comedy serials with 18 Years of broadcasting. Based on rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people, the series represents many political and social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavor. It is aired in Nepal Television at 8:50 PM and in YouTube at 9:30 PM every Tuesday. This show is produced by Media Hub Pvt. Ltd. 

The story is based on the rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people. The show represents many political as well as social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavour.

Based on rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people, the series represents many political and social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavor. It is aired in Nepal Television at 8:50 PM and in YouTube at 9:30 PM every Tuesday. This show is produced by Media Hub Pvt. Ltd. 

The story is based on the rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people. The show represents many political as well as social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavour.

snippet.title: Shops with NO Shopkeepers! Have seen this?
snippet.description:
Across New Zealand, you'll find unmanned shops that are based on honesty. Kiwi farmers set up stalls on the roadside outside their homes and sell their fruit and vegetables for low prices directly to motorists. The farmer isn't at the stall, though! An honesty box is there where customers leave the correct amount for what they take.

At this stall in Northland, we bought two bags of avocados for just $4. Does this happen in your country? We've also heard this happens in Mizoram, India.
